2.3	Drill down Enquiry
User to have following options in order to view drill down data.
•	Date – User to choose the date for enquiry
•	Report – User to select report either YSA, PNL or NWSA from the drop down.
•	Code – User will enter the code of the for which the data is required.
•	Scope – User to choose if the data required is for Bank Level, Circle Level or for a particular Branch.
o	Bank Level – the data will be shown for the consolidated for bank level.
o	Circle Level – the user needs to choose the circle for which the data is required. A drop down to be provided for selecting the circle.
o	Branch Level– in case user want to view data for a particular branch only, an input will be provided in enter the branch code.
•	Once the above required details are entered, user can fetch the data.




